      "description": "This investment-grade E46 M3 represents the zenith of naturally aspirated BMW M-Division engineering. At its heart lies the S54B32 inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a double-VANOS variable valve timing system that operates with factory-spec precision. The high-revving valvetrain remains perfectly shimmed, delivering linear power to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Structural integrity is paramount; the rear subframe mounting points are flawless, and the chassis retains its original torsional rigidity. Equipped with a GKN variable M differential lock and a pristine suspension geometry, this specimen offers the communicative feedback and telepathic handling expected of a showroom-quality icon. An absolute purist\u2019s example in concours condition.",
